===========
 POWERNICK 
===========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

plugin used to monitor log messages

| 

  relay log messages to nicks joined on the partyline (DCC CHAT) 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *powernick*

    :description: set powernick (gets /msg of bot logs)

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !powernick
        <output> test is not joined on the partylist .. make a dcc chat
        <output>  connection to the bot


2) *powernick-del*

    :description: remove powernick (gets

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !powernick-del
        <output> no powernick set


3) *powernick-list*

    :description: show power nicks in use

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !powernick-list
        <output> none
